# Class: gitea::packages
# ===========================
#
# Manages dependencies for the `::gitea` class.
#
# Parameters
# ----------
#
# * `dependencies_ensure`
# Should dependencies be installed? Defaults to 'present'.
#
# * `dependencies`
# List of OS family specific dependencies.
#
# Authors
# -------
#
# Daniel S. Reichenbach <daniel@kogitoapp.com>
#
# Copyright
# ---------
